RIGBY RANCH COMPANY, a Corporation, Debtor, v. ISLAND IMPROVEMENT COMPANY, a Corporation, et al. No. 1394. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. Aug. 28, 1936. Skeen & Skeen, of Salt Lake City, Utah, for appellant. W. Q. Van Cott, of Salt Lake City, Utah, for appellees.

Before LEWIS and McDERMOTT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed on stipulation.
